These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta
There 2 different types of food: avocado, pear
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | fanta  | iced-tea |
| Food       | avocado | pear |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | soy-milk |
| Sport      | rowing     | ice-hockey  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, adventure
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian
1. the japanese is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the japanese is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | adventure  |
| Nationality   | japanese | brazilian |

 #################################

 
